Class TeradataBufferedInserter

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.writer.commands.BaseJdbcBufferedInserter
      • gobblin.writer.commands.TeradataBufferedInserter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JdbcBufferedInserter

    public class TeradataBufferedInserter
extends BaseJdbcBufferedInserter
    The implementation of JdbcBufferedInserter for Teradata. Writing is done by executing JdbcBufferedInserter.WRITER_JDBC_INSERT_BATCH_SIZE sized batch inserts.
